    {
      "id": "HSVFdVyQ8HkxERpBR5aLX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -110.57142857142878,
      "y": 190.5370347764757,
      "width": 341.93975830078125,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1173277261,
      "version": 236,
      "versionNonce": 953319437,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783659777975,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "steps to startup :\n1. uv venv (virtual envi)\n2. pip install django\n3. django-admin startproject name \n4. python manage.py",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "steps to startup :\n1. uv venv (virtual envi)\n2. pip install django\n3. django-admin startproject name \n4. python manage.py",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "x3OukDqUm3iMEB8ZM-2qI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 526.0952380952378,
      "y": 203.87036810980896,
      "width": 955.2393188476562,
      "height": 725,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1745725933,
      "version": 141,
      "versionNonce": 2070981155,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783659638130,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Basic:\n1. settings.py\n2. settings.py\n\nProject ki saari settings aur configuration yahan hoti hai.\n\nurls.py - User kis URL pe aaya hai aur usko kis View ke paas bhejna hai, ye yahan decide hota hai.\n\nviews.py - User ki request ko process karke uske hisaab se response banata hai.\n\n📄 templates\n\nView se aaya hua data use karke Dynamic HTML page banata hai.\n\n🌐 Browser\n\nJo HTML mila hai usko user ko display karta hai.\n\n📦 Context\n\nView se Template me bheja gaya data (Dictionary).\n\n📨 Request\n\nBrowser/User ki taraf se server ko bheji gayi information.\n\n📤 Response\n\nServer ki taraf se Browser ko bheja gaya result (HTML/JSON/Text).",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Basic:\n1. settings.py\n2. settings.py\n\nProject ki saari settings aur configuration yahan hoti hai.\n\nurls.py - User kis URL pe aaya hai aur usko kis View ke paas bhejna hai, ye yahan decide hota hai.\n\nviews.py - User ki request ko process karke uske hisaab se response banata hai.\n\n📄 templates\n\nView se aaya hua data use karke Dynamic HTML page banata hai.\n\n🌐 Browser\n\nJo HTML mila hai usko user ko display karta hai.\n\n📦 Context\n\nView se Template me bheja gaya data (Dictionary).\n\n📨 Request\n\nBrowser/User ki taraf se server ko bheji gayi information.\n\n📤 Response\n\nServer ki taraf se Browser ko bheja gaya result (HTML/JSON/Text).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
