      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783659764389,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "settings.py - Project ki saari settings aur configuration yahan hoti hai.\nurls.py - User kis URL pe aaya hai aur usko kis View ke paas bhejna hai, ye yahan decide hota hai.\nviews.py - User ki request ko process karke uske hisaab se response banata hai.\ntemplates - View se aaya hua data use karke Dynamic HTML page banata hai.\nBrowser - Jo HTML mila hai usko user ko display karta hai.\nContext - View se Template me bheja gaya data (Dictionary).\nRequest - Browser/User ki taraf se server ko bheji gayi information.\nResponse - Server ki taraf se Browser ko bheja gaya result (HTML/JSON/Text).",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "settings.py - Project ki saari settings aur configuration yahan hoti hai.\nurls.py - User kis URL pe aaya hai aur usko kis View ke paas bhejna hai, ye yahan decide hota hai.\nviews.py - User ki request ko process karke uske hisaab se response banata hai.\ntemplates - View se aaya hua data use karke Dynamic HTML page banata hai.\nBrowser - Jo HTML mila hai usko user ko display karta hai.\nContext - View se Template me bheja gaya data (Dictionary).\nRequest - Browser/User ki taraf se server ko bheji gayi information.\nResponse - Server ki taraf se Browser ko bheja gaya result (HTML/JSON/Text).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
